sequenceDiagram
    participant MonitorSys as SecurityMonitoringSystem
    participant Admin as SystemAdmin
    participant Alert as SecurityAlert
    participant Handler as AlertHandler
    participant Device

    MonitorSys->>MonitorSys: Detect Anomaly
    MonitorSys->>Alert: Create Alert (Pending)
    MonitorSys-->>Admin: Notify Alert
    Admin->>Alert: View Details
    Admin->>Handler: Execute Response (Isolate)
    Handler->>Device: Isolate Command
    Device-->>Handler: Isolation Success
    Handler->>Alert: Update Status (Processed)
    Handler->>Alert: Add Log Entry
    Admin->>Alert: Close Alert
